{"tid":732860,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友放假無野做都唔覆機","createTime":"2018-07-07T09:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T11:33:12.000Z","uid":115904,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"dee44a52089904485f2e7c6b1ec4ee94ad499f2b","tid":732860,"uid":115904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:28:25.000Z","msg":"男朋友平日番工好忙，但一個上晝總會覆一次半次，下晝都係，我都好心滿意足<br />\n<br />\n但佢一放假就唔點覆機，五六個鐘都未必會覆，除左早晨之外亦好少會主動搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問過佢點解，佢話放假響屋企唔會玩電話，所以無覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有反映過，如果得閒覆下我都好呀，講完果個星期好啲之後又打回原形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平日我知佢辛苦，我地住得遠，放工我過去佢住果邊食飯睇戲都唔緊要（利申：自己都要番工）星期六日我通常都忙，但佢都唔會想出黎同我食下飯、見下我咁，但平時又講到成日掛住我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都係呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916546359741da727eb47bd38b409a0462386fe0","tid":732860,"uid":56498,"like":12,"dislike":19,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:31:01.000Z","msg":"放假自己hea下都唔比，一定要覆手機，你真係惡撚過共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf8dd5bda2432415cd54eb7eec556f7598e1d2c","tid":732860,"uid":22375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:31:54.000Z","msg":"有時放假後想hea下 咩都唔理"},{"pid":"84c5d53ca568f955de51a0a0da4d3b44e0fced0e","tid":732860,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:33:56.000Z","msg":"仲要黎做乜"},{"pid":"08e319032ae73ecd4290c19cb7eecc4b7c5e6908","tid":732860,"uid":67903,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:34:19.000Z","msg":"放假都要比人管<br />\n番工已經辛苦"},{"pid":"3c89812a2713ed2385d43a1bb8d7e8b9d9d22fc9","tid":732860,"uid":146435,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:34:24.000Z","msg":"放假又無得扑野 又要覆你 係男人都死啦"},{"pid":"67da13c307e2634f985371d9ba65722fb012ece3","tid":732860,"uid":81453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"佢放假有咩做先"},{"pid":"8737926068664dda2bf4ec1a3811b33eeed42488","tid":732860,"uid":47590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:37:14.000Z","msg":"男人放假係屋企都係打機居多<br />\n咁放假都係想做自己想做既野啫<br />\n你應該自己搵節目好過成日計住佢幾耐唔覆message<br />\n你調節唔到自己心態你自己有排唔開心<br />\n同埋有d男人真係放假好少禁電話<br />\n睇開d啦絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c847a08e6777b342b70282be47503be6ff61700","tid":732860,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"訓下教 打下機 俾個腦休息下都唔撚得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d2f3a2a9272c2861deedde878c3c78725c0013","tid":732860,"uid":193314,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"樓主都係掛住男朋友姐 <br />\n正常來講佢男朋友冇嘢做嘅話 都會好奇佢點解唔覆 佢一兩句"},{"pid":"5a2f9cdb1e8ba1de81d7e515e9192892a79447a4","tid":732860,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打機通常唔想理人，因為一覆就可能要覆成日。"},{"pid":"8e57148e73d9ddbd771a2b414fb7731fdb247108","tid":732860,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:49:10.000Z","msg":"唔玩電話，咁佢有冇講係屋企做咩？"},{"pid":"8a7f2db0a1da0e8732018acea1481232673e62f6","tid":732860,"uid":2546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:52:13.000Z","msg":"慣咗就得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男朋友都係咁 因為有工作wtsapp gp, 假期都會響<br />\n所以佢都慣咗由佢響唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放假都好少睇電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27402dd0107cbd3858cbb990054164fcfb99140","tid":732860,"uid":172244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"叫雞要同你講？"},{"pid":"415e375589bb04d698e46d90ee571d927a0ea7b9","tid":732860,"uid":132902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:56:12.000Z","msg":"佢同我返左大陸叫雞 咪阻住我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4242cd27bc32eebaffe7bd79dea16a0597634549","tid":732860,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:57:15.000Z","msg":"咁你都忙佢仲出嚟做乜"},{"pid":"73f2ffa7ef94655eb0de0d91a2b3c8a39d118812","tid":732860,"uid":3117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:57:21.000Z","msg":"有第條女又會同你講咩"},{"pid":"95e97f9a6ce7b62512bbb337f05217677b1748db","tid":732860,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"究竟呢個係基帖定港女帖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb4505e1bf47a13af5b13b60f34417574f8f52e","tid":732860,"uid":193314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a2f9cdb1e8ba1de81d7e515e9192892a79447a4","tid":732860,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打機通常唔想理人，因為一覆就可能要覆成日。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:15:32.000Z","msg":"咁起碼講左話打機 女仔都起碼放心啲 都知對方做緊乜嘛 <br />\n女仔就唔會諗歪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e5a5911250d79b50416338c2dd9f56684e6bfb","tid":732860,"uid":60982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:17:51.000Z","msg":"唔覆又噪 hea覆又噪 放假係咪都要攬住部電話"},{"pid":"4ae46ad4448694390fc676e3da7fea1b55017b5f","tid":732860,"uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:25:13.000Z",